This is a 'game' that is designed to test the features of WorldWeaver (WW).
Each room tests a different piece of functionality that the game engine
supports. To enter a testing room simply type in the room's name.
(No need to say 'go to' etc, just enter its name).

---

NOTE:
If you test the fighting features, the player should regain some more life
every 5 actions.

NOTE:
If you want to view the current time, use:
time
